text: Widi Dwinanda (born Cianjur, West Java on January 10, 1988) is an Indonesian actor, presenter and sportscaster. In 2015, she was awarded Commendable Female Actress for the category on Television Movies via Biopic Television Movies Ibu Een Guru Qolbu. == Filmography == === Film === Source: {| class="wikitable
